                <head>316. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On February 1, 1962, the Office of the <gloss target="#t_UN1">UN</gloss> High
                    Commissioner for Refugees announced that Prince <persName corresp="#p_AKS1"
                        >Sadruddin Aga Khan</persName> was appointed as Deputy <gloss
                        target="#t_UN1">UN</gloss> High Commissioner for Refugees. (Telegram 750
                    from Geneva, February 1, 1962; National Archives and Records Administration,
                        <gloss target="#t_RG1">RG</gloss> 59, Central Files 1960–63,
                    324.8411/2–162)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
